---
// Hero: ファーストビュー、キャッチコピー + DL ボタン + ネオン背景
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 600" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" class="hero-svg">
      <defs>
        <pattern id="grid-pattern" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,240,255,0.07)" stroke-width="1" />
        </pattern>
        <radialGradient id="glow" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="60%">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(79,108,255,0.4)" />
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(0,0,0,0)" />
        </radialGradient>
      </defs>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid-pattern)" />
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#glow)" />
      <!-- 流れる配線アニメーション -->
      <path
        d="M 0 200 L 200 200 L 200 350 L 500 350 L 500 150 L 800 150 L 800 400 L 1200 400"
        fill="none"
        stroke="var(--neon-cyan)"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-dasharray="8 4"
        opacity="0.5"
        class="flow-line"
      />
      <path
        d="M 1200 100 L 900 100 L 900 250 L 600 250 L 600 450 L 300 450 L 300 280 L 0 280"
        fill="none"
        stroke="var(--neon-magenta)"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-dasharray="6 6"
        opacity="0.4"
        class="flow-line flow-line-2"
      />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-inner">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">⚡ for 電気工事の職人さん</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      平面図に <span class="neon-cyan">配線</span> を描いて、
      <br />
      <span class="neon-magenta">拾い出し</span> までを 1/3 の時間で。
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-lead">
      元請けからの PDF 図面の上に電気記号を置いて、配線を引いて、数えて、出力する。
      <br />
      電気工事のためだけに作った、無料のデスクトップアプリです。
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#download" class="btn-primary">
        <span>β版を無料ダウンロード</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#game-wire" class="btn-secondary">
        <span>🎮 配線パズルで遊ぶ</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-meta">
      Windows 10/11 対応 · インストーラ約 12MB · 著作権 © 北嶺建設
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .hero-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .flow-line {
    animation: flow 8s linear infinite;
  }
  .flow-line-2 {
    animation: flow 12s linear infinite reverse;
  }
  @keyframes flow {
    0% { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
    100% { stroke-dashoffset: -100; }
  }

  .hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 720px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--neon-cyan);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .neon-cyan {
    color: var(--neon-cyan);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
  }
  .neon-magenta {
    color: var(--neon-magenta);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 45, 209, 0.4);
  }

  .hero-lead {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero {
      min-height: 90vh;
      padding: 60px 18px;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    .hero-cta .btn-primary,
    .hero-cta .btn-secondary {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
